# Design Rules

> **Contents:** Text & Typography ¬∑ Colors ¬∑ Animation Pacing ¬∑ Scene Transitions ¬∑ Layout Grid (Landscape / Vertical / Square) ¬∑ Layout Patterns ¬∑ Spacing ¬∑ Scene Duration ¬∑ SVG Layers ¬∑ Keyframes ¬∑ Common Render Errors

## Colors

Use `theme(name)` ‚Äî provides `t.BG / t.PRIMARY / t.SECONDARY / t.ACCENT / t.SUCCESS` automatically. See gen-canvas.md for the full theme list.


## Animation Pacing

1. **Every visible element: both `animIn` + `animOut`** ‚Äî no exceptions.
2. **Stagger: 300‚Äì500ms between elements per scene**, max 800ms.
3. **Duration by role:**

| Role | Entrance | Exit |
| ---- | -------- | ---- |
| Hero | 1200‚Äì1500ms | 700‚Äì900ms |
| Heading | 800‚Äì1000ms | 500‚Äì600ms |
| Subtitle | 600‚Äì800ms | 400‚Äì500ms |
| Body / Label | 400‚Äì600ms | 300‚Äì400ms |

4. **Easing:** `easeOut` entrances ¬∑ `easeIn` exits ¬∑ `easeInOut` loops.

## Scene Transitions

1. **500ms scene bleed** ‚Äî next scene's SVG backgrounds start 500ms before current text exits. Avoids black gaps.
2. **Transition duration: 400‚Äì600ms**, max 800ms.
3. **Max 2 effect types per video.** Limits: flash intensity ‚â§ 0.7, shake intensity ‚â§ 6.

### Canvas Formats

| Format | Size | buildCanvas | Scale | Use Case |
| ------ | ---- | ----------- | ----- | -------- |
| Landscape | 1920√ó1080 | default | 1.0 | YouTube, ads, presentations |
| Vertical | 1080√ó1920 | `width:1080, height:1920` | √ó0.7 | TikTok, Reels, Stories |
| Square | 1080√ó1080 | `width:1080, height:1080` | √ó0.8 | Instagram feed, LinkedIn |

Apply scale to all font sizes, element dimensions, and gaps when using non-default formats.

