### Layout Patterns

| Pattern | When to use | Structure |
| ------- | ----------- | --------- |
| **Full center** | Brand reveal, CTA | Heading ‚Üí divider ‚Üí subtitle vertically centered |
| **Hero + list** | Feature scenes | Heading (top 35%) + 3‚Äì4 body items (bottom 65%) |
| **Stat focus** | Social proof, data | `t.display` large number + subtitle label, centered |
| **Split 50/50** | Comparison, before/after | Left col text + Right col SVG/visual |
| **Timeline** | Process, steps | `svgStepIndicator` + body labels staggered down |

---

### Spacing Rules

- heading‚Üídivider: 5‚Äì10px ¬∑ divider‚Üísubtitle: 20‚Äì30px
- Between feature rows: 130‚Äì145px ¬∑ Between sections: 70‚Äì90px
- **Accent divider:** `makeShape("div", "rect", t.ACCENT, { x: 760, y, w: 400, h: 3 })`
- **Text over image/video:** `shadowBlur >= 8` or `strokeWidth: 1‚Äì2`

## Scene Duration & Pacing

| Scene Type | Duration | Element Stagger |
| ---------- | -------- | --------------- |
| Hero / brand | 4‚Äì6s | Title +500ms, subtitle +700ms |
| Feature | 5‚Äì7s | Items +300‚Äì500ms apart |
| Text-heavy | 6‚Äì8s | Allow reading time |
| CTA / closing | 4‚Äì6s | +800‚Äì1000ms for CTA button |

## SVG Background Layers

1. **2‚Äì4 helpers per scene**, max 5 (prevents shader compilation timeout).
2. **Opacity by depth:**

| Layer | Opacity | Examples |
| ----- | ------- | -------- |
| Far background | 0.03‚Äì0.06 | `svgDotGrid` ¬∑ `svgGridPattern` ¬∑ `svgLightStreak` |
| Mid background | 0.06‚Äì0.15 | `svgGradientOrb` ¬∑ `svgAurora` ¬∑ `svgHexGrid` |
| Foreground decoration | 0.2‚Äì0.5 | `svgParticles` ¬∑ `svgConfetti` ¬∑ `svgShootingStar` |
| UI overlay | 0.5‚Äì1.0 | `svgCheckMark` ¬∑ `svgBadgeStamp` ¬∑ `svgArrowPointer` |

3. **Global layers** (`svgVignette`, `svgDotGrid`) span `0‚ÄìmaxTime`. Vignette opacity: 0.5‚Äì0.7.

## Keyframes

1. **Position keyframe initial `{x, y}` must exactly match element placement** ‚Äî mismatches cause frame-1 jumps.
2. **Prefer `scale`/`opacity` keyframes** for subtle motion. Amplitude: scale ¬±0.02‚Äì0.03, opacity ¬±0.15‚Äì0.20.
3. **3‚Äì5 tracks per video**, max 8.

## Common Render Errors

| Error | Cause | Fix |
| ----- | ----- | --- |
| Shader timeout | Too many SVG layers with blur on same frame | ‚â§ 4 SVGs per scene, lower opacity |
| Font not found | Name mismatch in `fontAssets` | Check exact spelling |
| Blank/black video | `isVisible` missing on tracks | Use `autoTracks` (auto-sets) |
| Elements cut off | `maxTime` < last element end | Set `maxTime` >= largest end time |
| Flickering | Overlapping elements on same track | `autoTracks` splits them automatically |
